** Seussical Jr.
------------------------------------------------------------


** Columbus Children's Theater
------------------------------------------------------------

June 8th-19th

All of your favorite Dr. Seuss characters spring to life onstage in a fantastical musical extravaganza. The Cat in the Hat tells the story of Horton the elephant who discovers a speck of dust containing tiny people called the Whos. Horton must protect the Whos from a world of naysayers and dangers. Ultimately, the powers of friendship, loyalty, family, and community are challenged and emerge triumphant!

Event Website >> (http://www.columbuschildrenstheatre.org/seussical-jr.html)

