** FountainSide:Catch A Cloud
------------------------------------------------------------


** Scioto Mile
------------------------------------------------------------

All summer long!

It’s a whirlwind at FountainSide! Begin the day with mini-cloud creations at COSI on Wheels. Get crafty with Indian Village Outdoor Education Center and Macaroni Kid while learning about clouds and tornadoes. Catch a cloud in your hand with ACS Kids & Chemistry, and fly out of the park with Krash the “krazy” parrot from the Columbus Clippers. Discover how vegetables can protect one another with Local Matters and don’t forget to be a part of Lowe’s Plant and Grow workshop. Finally, be sure to visit OSU Sports Marketing to get active throughout the summer and top off your day with a smoothie from the Molina Healthcare Smoothie Bicycle, or a treat from the Sunny 95/Meijer Treat Truck.

Event Website >> (http://www.sciotomile.com/event-listing/fountainside-7-8-2015/)

